            <h3>Core Tactical Principles</h3>
            <ul class="tips-list">
                <li><strong>Operator Synergy:</strong> Combine operators with complementary abilities - e.g., a breacher paired with a recon operator for information gathering before pushing.</li>
                <li><strong>Loadout Balance:</strong> Ensure your team has a mix of offensive, defensive, and utility operators. Don't load everyone with the same weapon type.</li>
                <li><strong>Information Control:</strong> Use recon operators (Sledge, Twitch) to gather intel before committing your main force.</li>
                <li><strong>Area Denial:</strong> Deploy area denial operators (Mute, Kaid) strategically to control key choke points and objective areas.</li>
            </ul>

