            <p>A balanced Bandit team typically includes:</p>
            <ul class="tips-list">
                <li><strong>1-2 Breachers:</strong> Operators like Ash, Blitz, or Sledge to open paths and create entry points.</li>
                <li><strong>1 Recon Operator:</strong> Twitch or Mute for information gathering and area denial.</li>
                <li><strong>1 Support/Utility:</strong> Kaid or another operator with unique abilities that benefit the team.</li>
                <li><strong>2-3 Main Force:</strong> Operators with strong offensive capabilities and versatile loadouts.</li>
